reviewText: These two movies are by far two of the worst movies that my poor old eyes ever saw!!!  If I produced these movies, I would hang my head in shame and change my name! I feel as if I am just not articulate enough to describe my contempt for such poorly made movies and to think, these people actually got paid to act in them.  So folks, please stay clear of these two movies...they may be hazardous to your health!!!!!!!
